      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIRE WATER BURN (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Latest effort finished 3rd over 461m at this track beaten 3.5 lengths (26.15) behind Trick in a Grade 4/5 on July 2. Expected to go close with a clean break. LIFE IS YOURS (7) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten one length (19.39) behind Zari Exact at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and gets his chance. SCOOBY DANGER (3) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 10 lengths seventh (26.65) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track over 461m. Has the ability and looks a key chance. VISTA EXAM (2) looks an each-way chance.",
